STEPS
-----

- Remove any existing build

- Update translations (run message.sh)

- Set version # to metadata.desktop.template and metadata.desktop 

- Update changelog (from git log)

- Update README if needed -- TODO

- Build with cmake

- (OPTIONAL) To manually create mo files: msgfmt el.po --output-file el.mo


kNewHostStuff packaging (not in plasma 5 due to translations issue)
-----------------------

- Add any new language to kNewHostStuff.sh script

- Create "Get new hot stuff" package (run kNewHostStuff.sh) 

- Rename distrowatcher.plasmoid to a version specific file (e.g. distrowatcher_0.10.1.plasmoid)

Debian packaging (OPTIONAL) 
----------------

- Set version to deb.CMakeLists.txt

- Copy deb.CMakeLists.txt to CMakeLists.txt 

- Build deb package

- Revert gen.CMakeLists.txt to CMakeLists.txt

- Tag the new version --TODO
